Mason Capital Management, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 22, 2017 7:10 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Mason Capital Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Mason Capital Management, LLC is a privately owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pension and profit sharing plans, pooled investment vehicles, and living trusts. It invests in the public equity and hedging markets of the United States. Mason Capital Management was founded in 2000 and is based in New York, New York.


110 East 59th Street30th FloorNew York, NY 10022United StatesFounded in 2000



Phone: 212-771-1206

Fax: 212-644-4264

www.masoncap.com







