 MASON CAPITAL Overview



												   Mason Capital Management Llc is a hedge fund that manages 12.7 BN dollars in regulatory AUM and has 28 employees, of which 18 perform investment advisory functions. The manager's has disclosed holdings from 12/31/02 to 03/31/17. The fund's latest filing disclosed 641MM in positions, representing 5% of the manager's regulatory AUM.
												



